caption:
Societal expectations about what your body should look like will come and go with fashions and trends. But your body will be with you for life. So rebel against all those marketing campaigns aimed at making you feel like you need to look different and bravely give your body the respect it deserves. 

Unfollow accounts that make you feel ugly and instead follow some of the incredible accounts that are uplifting, inspiring and empowering women to embrace and look after their bodies. 

